{"tid":86194,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超GG了！雲格勢續約2年","createTime":"2017-01-19T01:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T07:18:39.000Z","uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef63d34e9eece8f0b9f67ebdbb6d9b05d2f051be","tid":86194,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"雲格繼續做多2年領隊，唔知阿仙奴球迷點睇呢？英國《鏡報》報道，為盡快完成奧斯爾及阿歷斯山齊士，兵工廠高層將於3月尾同雲格續約，換言之雲格會教到2019年。唔少槍迷都不滿雲格「年年爭第4」嘅心態，好想愛隊作出轉變，但阿仙奴高層似乎冇咁嘅諗法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今季阿仙奴陸續同陣中球員續約，依家最難搞嘅係奧燒同A山。早前奧燒就同德國傳媒講過，好想繼續留效，但佢好着重恩師雲格嘅去向，換言之如果雲格離開，奧斯爾亦勢必他投。兵工廠好睇重呢2名星級主將，奧斯爾呢番說話，絕對為雲格爭番唔少分數。《鏡報》表示，阿仙奴將於3月22號國際賽英格蘭對德國咁上下時間，同雲格續約2年，如果呢個消息係真，唔少「反雲」球迷肯定好失望。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"2be98787e038a79255bc2a08d24703177621ebd7","tid":86194,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"阿妓GG渣嘛，關人撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add8821c30aaba2949f0faf67d42e29769e87269","tid":86194,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b9f367ee0d93488bfb91e45977ba74e33dd402","tid":86194,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正"},{"pid":"e19cb3160db453c8d7af401e2be4d61ba8cbb56f","tid":86194,"uid":25067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"教到插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612f78b70fbea8039d685b218d6937946eae8b9a","tid